Package: yaamake
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, yaamake-makefiles
Recommends: git
Description: Makefile system to build and program AVR projects
 Yaamake is handy makefile system to be used with gnu make
 for building and programming AVR projects. IT allows you to
 write simple Makefile with few variable definitions and
 upplies lot of defined targets (actions).
 .
 Yaamake is mainly used by Yaal project, but it's also
 very useful separately.
 .
 This package contains tool to find location of actual makefiles.

Package: yaamake-doc
Architecture: all
Description: documentation for yaamake
